."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This makes a lovely host gift or as a special treat to friends and family at Christmas time.","For added crunch, add 50 g coarsely chopped chocolate pieces to the mixture in step 6, then proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","3h 10m","25 piece"]}